</code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">11</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>municipality
may, upon approval of the electors of the </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">12</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>municipality pursuant to
subsection (b) of this Section, impose </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">13</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>by ordinance or resolution the tax authorized in Sections </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">14</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>8-11-1.3, 8-11-1.4 and 8-11-1.5 of this Act.</code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">15</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code>(b) The corporate authorities of the municipality may by </code></td></tr><tr><td class="number">16</td><td class="junk"></td><td class="xsl" ><code>ordinance or
